{"title_page": "2013 World Taekwondo Championships \u2013 Women's featherweight", "text_new": "{{short description|Taekwondo competition}}\n{{2013 World Taekwondo Championships}}\n{{main article|2013 World Taekwondo Championships}}\n\nThe '''women's featherweight''' is a competition featured at the [[2013 World Taekwondo Championships]], and was held at the Exhibition Center of Puebla in [[Puebla, Puebla|Puebla]], [[Mexico]] on July 20. Featherweights were limited to a maximum of 57 kilograms in body mass.\n\n==Medalists==\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n|bgcolor=\"gold\"|'''Gold'''||{{flagmedalist|[[Kim So-hee (taekwondo, born 1992)|Kim So-hee]]|KOR}}\n|-\n|bgcolor=\"silver\"|'''Silver'''||{{flagmedalist|[[Mayu Hamada]]|JPN}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"#cc9966\"|'''Bronze'''||{{flagmedalist|[[Anna-Lena Fr\u00f6mming]]|GER}}\n|-\n|{{flagmedalist|[[Eva Calvo (taekwondo)|Eva Calvo]]|ESP}}\n|}\n\n==Results==\n*'''DQ''' \u2014 Won by disqualification\n*'''W''' \u2014 Won by withdrawal\n\n===Finals===\n\n{{4TeamBracket-Compact-NoSeeds-Byes\n| RD1=Semifinals\n| RD2=Final\n| team-width=195\n| score-width=30\n| RD1-seed01=&nbsp;\n| RD1-team01={{flagathlete|[[Anna-Lena Fr\u00f6mming]]|GER}}\n| RD1-score01=7\n| RD1-seed02=&nbsp;\n| RD1-team02='''{{flagathlete|[[Kim So-hee (taekwondo, born 1992)|Kim So-hee]]|KOR}}'''\n| RD1-score02='''13'''\n| RD1-seed03=&nbsp;\n| RD1-team03={{flagathlete|[[Eva Calvo (taekwondo)|Eva Calvo]]|ESP}}\n| RD1-score03=2\n| RD1-seed04=7\n| RD1-team04='''{{flagathlete|[[Mayu Hamada]]|JPN}}'''\n| RD1-score04='''3'''\n| RD2-seed01=&nbsp;\n| RD2-team01='''{{flagathlete|[[Kim So-hee (taekwondo, born 1992)|Kim So-hee]]|KOR}}'''\n| RD2-score01='''15'''\n| RD2-seed02=7\n| RD2-team02={{flagathlete|[[Mayu Hamada]]|JPN}}\n| RD2-score02=8\n}}\n\n===Top half===\n\n====Section 1====\n{{16TeamBracket-Compact-NoSeeds-Byes\n| RD1=Round of 64\n| RD2=Round of 32\n| RD3=Round of 16\n| RD4=Quarterfinals\n| team-width=195\n| score-width=30\n\n| RD1-seed03=&nbsp;\n| RD1-team